#

Spicy Sriracha Honey Garlic Chicken

$15.99
600 kcal

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

DinnerQuick MealSavory

Description

A sweet and spicy chicken dish that packs a punch with flavor and is perfect for any night of the week.

Ingredients

  • Chicken thighs: 1 lb
  • Sriracha sauce: 1/4 cup
  • Honey: 2 tbsp
  • Garlic cloves: 4, minced
  • Soy sauce: 2 tbsp
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Green onions: 2, chopped
  • Sesame seeds: 1 tbsp
